{
  "id": "63e4555812857a001b8fcaf4",
  "title": "先送りは未来から心の安寧を前借りしてるだけ",
  "created": 1675908442,
  "updated": 1675908579,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "63e4555812857a001b8fcaf4",
      "text": "先送りは未来から心の安寧を前借りしてるだけ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675908442,
      "updated": 1675908460
    },
    {
      "id": "63e45580aff09e00001aad5c",
      "text": "書籍「[ポモドーロテクニック入門]」の読書メモから",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675908480,
      "updated": 1675908510
    },
    {
      "id": "63e45580aff09e00001aad5d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675908480,
      "updated": 1675908480
    },
    {
      "id": "63e45559aff09e00001aad51",
      "text": "from [レバレッジメモ:ポモドーロテクニック入門]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675908442,
      "updated": 1675908476
    },
    {
      "id": "63e45559aff09e00001aad52",
      "text": " [先送り]はなぜ起きるか",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675908442,
      "updated": 1675908538
    },
    {
      "id": "63e455b9aff09e00001aad5e",
      "text": " ストレスがある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675908538,
      "updated": 1675908541
    },
    {
      "id": "63e45559aff09e00001aad53",
      "text": " \t他人にやらされている感",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675908442,
      "updated": 1675908544
    },
    {
      "id": "63e45559aff09e00001aad54",
      "text": " \t完璧でなきゃというプレッシャー",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675908442,
      "updated": 1675908544
    },
    {
      "id": "63e45559aff09e00001aad55",
      "text": " \t失敗したり批判を受けたりすることに対する恐怖",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675908442,
      "updated": 1675908546
    },
    {
      "id": "63e45559aff09e00001aad56",
      "text": " 先送りをすると、一時的にこれらのストレスから解放される。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675908442,
      "updated": 1675908520
    },
    {
      "id": "63e45559aff09e00001aad57",
      "text": " \tこれが精神的な報酬になってしまうせいで「先送り」という行動が強化されてしまう。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675908442,
      "updated": 1675908520
    },
    {
      "id": "63e45559aff09e00001aad58",
      "text": " \tしかしこれは[未来から心の安寧を前借り]しているだけ。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675908442,
      "updated": 1675908520
    },
    {
      "id": "63e45559aff09e00001aad59",
      "text": " \t借りれば借りるほど利息がついて苦しくなる。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675908442,
      "updated": 1675908520
    },
    {
      "id": "63e45559aff09e00001aad5a",
      "text": " ストレスは自分の内部から起こるもの。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675908442,
      "updated": 1675908520
    },
    {
      "id": "63e45559aff09e00001aad5b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675908442,
      "updated": 1675908442
    },
    {
      "id": "63e455ceaff09e00001aad5f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675908559,
      "updated": 1675908559
    },
    {
      "id": "63e455ceaff09e00001aad60",
      "text": "[心の安寧] [安寧] [ストレスフリー] [ストレスレス]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675908559,
      "updated": 1675908579
    },
    {
      "id": "63e455cfaff09e00001aad61",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675908559,
      "updated": 1675908559
    }
  ]
}